&lt;p&gt;As a DevOps Engineer supporting operations on site at Joint Base Lewis–McChord in Tacoma, WA, you are the tactical edge of our engineering team. You aren’t just maintaining a platform; you play a key role in the technical success of a project. You will interface directly with customers to understand their unique constraints—such as restricted networks, hardware limitations, or urgent operational requirements—and tailor our automation and deployment strategies to move the needle for them.&lt;/p&gt;
